summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5092 for the improvement of Lucile Street, from 1st Avenue South to Duwamish Avenue; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 58548, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
